            "title": "蕭正楠第一次為兒子操刀剪髮  黃翠如笑爆︰好彩你未識得照鏡",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"蕭正楠第一次為兒子操刀剪髮  黃翠如笑爆︰好彩你未識得照鏡\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5ea49b508b87fc0114c54edaec92d0ff/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050816415662358.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">蕭正楠第一次為兒子操刀剪髮  黃翠如笑爆︰好彩你未識得照鏡</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>43歲黃翠如和48歲的蕭正楠今年3月成功誕下一名兒子「蕭哈哈」，組成幸福的一家三口。兩公婆有子萬事足，不時在社交網分享生活點滴。今日（8日）黃翠如在社交網透露，兒子出世一個多月頭髮變長，新手爸爸蕭正楠化身髮型師，親自操刀為兒子剪髮。\n\n</p><h2>蕭哈哈頭髮製作肖像圖案</h2>\n<p>蕭正楠膽粗粗首次為兒子剪頭髮，不過，似乎技術麻麻，黃翠如笑言︰「哈爸給BB剪第一束毛的一天。哈爸一直說哈哈兩邊的頭髮比較長，要給他修剪一下，哈媽特意去弄起手工來，好好紀念哈哈的第一剪。當然沒有想到，哈爸的剪髮技巧，是這樣......哈哈，這是你爸爸給你的第一個髮型。好彩你仲未識得照鏡﹗」蕭正楠就留言向兒子道歉說︰「哈哈對不起，我會自己剪番自己。」\n\n</p>\n<p>而相中更見黃翠如為了紀念兒子剪下來的第一撮頭髮，她把胎毛DIY製作成BB肖像圖案，非常可愛，極具心思。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237134/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蕭正楠首次為兒子剪頭髮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b053163682dc9772e15ea35892dea66/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_16_13_04_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蕭正楠首次為兒子剪頭髮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237135/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃翠如在社交網表示，兒子出世一個多月頭髮變長。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/77399ad8f6f5d5db8ea2fb88f7d40d01/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_16_13_04_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃翠如在社交網表示，兒子出世一個多月頭髮變長。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237136/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/286802f666bfe061e0850310a221f0f2/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_16_13_04_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237137/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蕭正楠為愛兒修剪的第一個髮型。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/73b976e230facf9cc0d766f4e078251f/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_16_13_04_4_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蕭正楠為愛兒修剪的第一個髮型。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237138/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"新髮型好有漫畫風，翠如把頭髮設計成嬰兒圖案留念。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d19e83bcadaf4c678aca610f1a663c82/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_16_13_04_5_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        新髮型好有漫畫風，翠如把頭髮設計成嬰兒圖案留念。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237139/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"片段中可見蕭正楠嗅BB頭髮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19a70680e7a05c5b5db4a7b4309e7705/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_16_13_04_6_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        片段中可見蕭正楠嗅BB頭髮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237140/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"手起刀落！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d6927c2e9811a827d35df73f5588d25e/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_16_13_04.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        手起刀落！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-sl